WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.030
Well, good evening family. Thank you for

00:00:03.040 --> 00:00:04.950
joining us again tonight, and good

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:06.990
morning to all of you in Australia. I don't

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:09.430
know what time it is over there, but I

00:00:09.440 --> 00:00:10.870
like to say good morning all the time, even when

00:00:10.870 --> 00:00:10.880
it is

00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:12.870
not morning.

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:15.670
We have a lot to talk about

00:00:15.680 --> 00:00:18.590
tonight. We have these clips

00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:21.510
Braden made for us, and he'll be adding

00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:24.710
new things to the back of the screen. He

00:00:24.720 --> 00:00:26.750
works so hard at it. I told him,

00:00:26.760 --> 00:00:28.630
'Let's do two nights in a row of that.'He

00:00:28.630 --> 00:00:28.640
worked

00:00:28.640 --> 00:00:30.910
so hard on

00:00:30.920 --> 00:00:35.030
the prophetic

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:37.390
mural.

00:00:37.400 --> 00:00:38.790
It's needed,

00:00:38.790 --> 00:00:38.800
even though

00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:41.350
my head's covering all of it.

00:00:41.360 --> 00:00:42.830
Well, you weren't here last night,

00:00:42.840 --> 00:00:44.270
that's why. But I'd rather have you here

00:00:44.280 --> 00:00:45.910
than that.

00:00:45.920 --> 00:00:49.950
Come get closer to me.

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:52.990
Let's go over some of the things

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:55.190
in the news.

00:00:55.200 --> 00:00:56.870
I want to

00:00:56.880 --> 00:00:59.470
start right off by saying this:

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:02.510
I thought it was amazing last

00:01:02.520 --> 00:01:03.670
night

00:01:03.680 --> 00:01:06.190
because I went over everything

00:01:06.200 --> 00:01:07.870
the Lord showed us at the end of the

00:01:07.880 --> 00:01:09.350
broadcast—when

00:01:09.360 --> 00:01:11.150
it happened, how it happened, and

00:01:11.160 --> 00:01:14.790
everything.

00:01:14.800 --> 00:01:17.710
Excuse me, that's why I'm

00:01:17.720 --> 00:01:20.310
sitting. I just had greasy food.

00:01:20.320 --> 00:01:27.070
I took a bite of that bread.

00:01:27.080 --> 00:01:31.270
It wasn't until

00:01:31.280 --> 00:01:32.870
I said,

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:35.430
'Don't you see? I can't do anything.

00:01:35.440 --> 00:01:37.470
I don't have control of it,'and it

00:01:37.480 --> 00:01:38.990
was a flatline. It was like touching a

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:41.630
cold stove last night.

00:01:41.640 --> 00:01:45.350
But the moment I gave Jesus the praise,

00:01:45.360 --> 00:01:49.790
the moment I acknowledged him,

00:01:49.800 --> 00:01:52.350
it switched on and I

00:01:52.360 --> 00:01:54.710
started seeing.

00:01:54.720 --> 00:01:58.150
He said, 'If you give me praise and glory

00:01:58.160 --> 00:02:00.110
and touch not the glory,

00:02:00.120 --> 00:02:02.030
touch not the anointing,

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:04.590
every time you do this, I'll show up

00:02:04.600 --> 00:02:06.270
like

00:02:06.270 --> 00:02:06.280
that.'But

00:02:06.280 --> 00:02:07.830
last night I didn't, because I don't

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:08.950
want to be redundant. It's like

00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:10.950
repeating things over and over

00:02:10.960 --> 00:02:13.470
again. Brandon can't do anything apart

00:02:13.480 --> 00:02:14.710
from him.

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:17.270
Anything I see, anything that's shown to

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:19.350
us by the spirit of God, is all

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:21.110
because of God.

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:22.750
I say it every single time and I'll

00:02:22.760 --> 00:02:25.150
continue to say it. Last night was a

00:02:25.160 --> 00:02:26.950
perfect example.

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:28.870
I avoided trying to go over it, and there

00:02:28.870 --> 00:02:28.880
it was—it

00:02:28.880 --> 00:02:30.870
was a flatline.

00:02:30.880 --> 00:02:32.510
I did the whole broadcast and showed

00:02:32.520 --> 00:02:34.590
you all the things until

00:02:34.600 --> 00:02:36.790
I said, 'Well, excuse me,

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:38.510
here we are

00:02:38.510 --> 00:02:38.520
folks.'I

00:02:38.520 --> 00:02:40.390
thought it was amazing because the moment I

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:42.870
gave him acknowledgement,

00:02:42.880 --> 00:02:46.670
the moment I said it out of my

00:02:46.670 --> 00:02:46.680
mouth—apart

00:02:46.680 --> 00:02:49.470
from him, I can do nothing;

00:02:49.480 --> 00:02:52.950
we give all the glory to

00:02:52.950 --> 00:02:52.960
Jesus—I

00:02:52.960 --> 00:02:56.630
started seeing instantaneously.

00:02:56.640 --> 00:02:58.470
It was amazing.

00:03:00.560 --> 00:03:02.550
The broadcast went on for three hours.

00:03:02.560 --> 00:03:05.390
I said I couldn't get in the river

00:03:05.400 --> 00:03:07.550
no matter how hard I tried.

00:03:07.560 --> 00:03:10.150
Even today, whenever he took me

00:03:10.160 --> 00:03:11.590
and I was

00:03:11.600 --> 00:03:13.390
in my prayer time, he said,

00:03:13.390 --> 00:03:13.400
'Brandon'—I

00:03:13.400 --> 00:03:15.350
said, 'What is going on? How

00:03:15.350 --> 00:03:15.360
are

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:16.630
things going

00:03:16.630 --> 00:03:16.640
today?'just

00:03:16.640 --> 00:03:17.950
talking like I always do to him. And he

00:03:17.960 --> 00:03:19.070
said, 'Brandon, I want you to start

00:03:19.080 --> 00:03:22.550
enjoying life more.

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:25.630
You're taking too much of this on you.

00:03:25.640 --> 00:03:29.470
I want you to have fun and enjoy

00:03:29.470 --> 00:03:29.480
life.'I

00:03:29.480 --> 00:03:34.150
said, 'I get

00:03:34.150 --> 00:03:34.160
it.'He

00:03:34.160 --> 00:03:35.750
said, 'Tell my people to have more

00:03:35.760 --> 00:03:38.150
fun.

00:03:38.160 --> 00:03:41.590
Tell my people to enjoy life more.

00:03:41.600 --> 00:03:44.950
Life's supposed to be fun and good.

00:03:44.960 --> 00:03:46.910
I gave you life, and life more

00:03:46.920 --> 00:03:48.910
abundantly.'So

00:03:48.920 --> 00:03:51.430
many people are

00:03:51.440 --> 00:03:53.870
like me—the pressure of life, the

00:03:53.880 --> 00:03:55.390
pressure of

00:03:55.400 --> 00:03:57.790
the prophetic, the pressure of all of it

00:03:57.800 --> 00:04:01.270
tries to choke the fun out of things.

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:02.670
He said, 'I want you just to have

00:04:02.680 --> 00:04:05.550
fun.

00:04:05.560 --> 00:04:08.790
Laugh more. Enjoy your family more.

00:04:08.800 --> 00:04:11.310
You don't have to

00:04:11.320 --> 00:04:13.230
walk under the

00:04:13.240 --> 00:04:14.870
pressure of things.

00:04:14.880 --> 00:04:17.150
It's not yours to

00:04:17.150 --> 00:04:17.160
carry.'Yesterday

00:04:17.160 --> 00:04:19.550
was a prime example of it.

00:04:19.560 --> 00:04:21.789
I remember Rodney Howard-Browne telling

00:04:21.799 --> 00:04:25.590
a story—and I don't talk about names,

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:27.270
but I remember this story. He brought it

00:04:27.280 --> 00:04:30.030
up to me where he was over at some

00:04:30.040 --> 00:04:32.950
pastor's house before the service and he

00:04:32.960 --> 00:04:36.150
was playing video games with

00:04:36.160 --> 00:04:38.710
the pastor's son. The pastor got

00:04:38.720 --> 00:04:41.790
so upset that he was not praying before

00:04:41.800 --> 00:04:44.590
the service;

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:46.830
he was not taking it more seriously in his

00:04:46.840 --> 00:04:47.910
mind.

00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:49.990
But Rodney felt to play the game with

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:51.750
the son,

00:04:51.760 --> 00:04:53.670
and the glory fell in

00:04:53.680 --> 00:04:56.150
that service.

00:04:56.150 --> 00:04:56.160
The

00:04:56.160 --> 00:04:58.470
bottom line

00:04:58.470 --> 00:04:58.480
is,

00:04:58.480 --> 00:05:01.590
it is in us. Regardless of

00:05:01.590 --> 00:05:01.600
whether

00:05:01.600 --> 00:05:03.510
you're having fun and enjoying life,

00:05:03.510 --> 00:05:03.520
or

00:05:03.520 --> 00:05:05.070
you're relaxing and

00:05:05.080 --> 00:05:07.190
resting, there's a point where you think

00:05:07.200 --> 00:05:08.870
it's self-righteousness that brings the

00:05:08.880 --> 00:05:10.150
glory.

00:05:10.160 --> 00:05:11.870
'Well, it's because I fasted

00:05:11.880 --> 00:05:13.350
five

00:05:13.360 --> 00:05:15.270
times this week,'and 'It's

00:05:15.280 --> 00:05:17.910
because I put myself in

00:05:17.910 --> 00:05:17.920
position.'Not

00:05:17.920 --> 00:05:20.190
saying that doesn't help your flesh

00:05:20.200 --> 00:05:22.310
to be crucified,

00:05:22.320 --> 00:05:24.670
but if you have the mindset

00:05:24.680 --> 00:05:26.670
that it's because of what I did that got

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:29.310
me qualified to get this,

00:05:29.320 --> 00:05:31.830
you already disqualified

00:05:31.840 --> 00:05:33.070
yourself.

00:05:33.080 --> 00:05:36.190
The Lord was showing me it's about

00:05:36.200 --> 00:05:38.430
relationship.

00:05:38.440 --> 00:05:39.270
He said, 'Brandon, it's about

00:05:39.270 --> 00:05:39.280
relationship.'Do

00:05:39.280 --> 00:05:41.030
you realize it's

00:05:41.040 --> 00:05:44.590
not about how much you

00:05:44.590 --> 00:05:44.600
think—'I

00:05:44.600 --> 00:05:46.750
didn't say anything rude

00:05:46.760 --> 00:05:48.830
today to Diana; I tried really hard

00:05:48.840 --> 00:05:50.790
to always walk in

00:05:50.790 --> 00:05:50.800
love'—when

00:05:50.800 --> 00:05:52.230
you're in

00:05:52.230 --> 00:05:52.240
a

00:05:52.240 --> 00:05:54.030
marriage

00:05:54.030 --> 00:05:54.040
and

00:05:54.040 --> 00:05:56.830
you work with somebody seven days

00:05:56.840 --> 00:05:57.910
a week,

00:05:57.920 --> 00:05:59.950
24 hours a day,

00:05:59.960 --> 00:06:01.990
you have a tendency to be cranky and

00:06:03.070 --> 00:06:03.080
crunchy.

00:06:04.640 --> 00:06:06.590
I tell her,

00:06:06.600 --> 00:06:08.510
'It's not about even

00:06:08.510 --> 00:06:08.520
that.''Well,

00:06:08.520 --> 00:06:10.310
I disqualified myself today; I had

00:06:10.320 --> 00:06:11.630
a bad attitude.'You always want to

00:06:11.640 --> 00:06:13.310
walk in love, but that's not the point. I'm

00:06:13.320 --> 00:06:14.670
trying

00:06:21.320 --> 00:06:23.830
to say that it's not how good

00:06:23.840 --> 00:06:26.190
you think you are that qualifies you for

00:06:26.200 --> 00:06:28.310
the glory.

00:06:28.320 --> 00:06:29.750
You're human,

00:06:29.760 --> 00:06:33.070
and you always lean on him.

00:06:33.080 --> 00:06:35.190
You are always leaning on and trusting

00:06:35.200 --> 00:06:36.230
in him

00:06:36.240 --> 00:06:39.430
regardless of how messed up you are.

00:06:39.440 --> 00:06:42.070
It's all about Jesus.

00:06:42.080 --> 00:06:43.990
It's just

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:47.470
a mindset of relationship

00:06:47.470 --> 00:06:47.480
that

00:06:47.480 --> 00:06:49.030
he's been teaching me about.

00:06:49.030 --> 00:06:49.040
It's

00:06:49.040 --> 00:06:50.630
always something like,

00:06:50.640 --> 00:06:53.030
'Well, I prayed extra long

00:06:53.040 --> 00:06:55.070
today.'We

00:06:55.080 --> 00:06:57.670
drove a lot more today and looked for

00:06:57.680 --> 00:07:00.310
stuff for our eBay store. 'You prayed

00:07:00.320 --> 00:07:02.350
a lot longer today, Brandon. Boy, I bet

00:07:02.360 --> 00:07:03.990
tonight's broadcast is going to be over

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:05.910
the top because you prayed in tongues

00:07:05.920 --> 00:07:08.550
for six hours.

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:09.710
I bet

00:07:09.710 --> 00:07:09.720
you're

00:07:09.720 --> 00:07:11.510
qualified tonight,

00:07:11.510 --> 00:07:11.520
buddy.'That's

00:07:11.520 --> 00:07:12.910
why the Lord told me,

00:07:12.920 --> 00:07:14.190
'Brandon,

00:07:14.200 --> 00:07:17.270
even on your worst day, it's my grace.

00:07:17.280 --> 00:07:18.750
No matter how much you have it in your

00:07:18.760 --> 00:07:20.550
mind to think that you're qualified

00:07:20.560 --> 00:07:22.630
tonight to see and be able to do

00:07:22.640 --> 00:07:25.350
anything in the spirit realm with me,

00:07:25.360 --> 00:07:26.950
you never were good enough in the first

00:07:26.960 --> 00:07:28.470
place. It was always by my grace and by

00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:30.310
the

00:07:30.310 --> 00:07:30.320
blood.'It

00:07:30.320 --> 00:07:32.430
goes back to

00:07:32.430 --> 00:07:32.440
when

00:07:32.440 --> 00:07:34.150
I stepped on the dog and killed

00:07:34.150 --> 00:07:34.160
it.

00:07:34.160 --> 00:07:35.750
If

00:07:35.750 --> 00:07:35.760
anyone

00:07:35.760 --> 00:07:36.950
hasn't heard that

00:07:36.960 --> 00:07:38.190
before,

00:07:38.200 --> 00:07:39.870
my little girl got a dog for

00:07:39.880 --> 00:07:41.470
Christmas.

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:44.310
Diana,

00:07:45.400 --> 00:07:46.830
I'm glad you're here; you can

00:07:46.840 --> 00:07:47.990
chime in.

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:49.630
Don't sit over there and be quiet. I

00:07:51.440 --> 00:07:53.750
was playing

00:07:53.760 --> 00:07:55.910
Warzone, Call of Duty, with Braden for

00:07:55.920 --> 00:07:57.350
Christmas.

00:07:57.360 --> 00:07:59.830
I'm really competitive and

00:07:59.840 --> 00:08:02.790
we like to win. Braden's really good

00:08:02.800 --> 00:08:05.310
at Call of Duty.

00:08:05.310 --> 00:08:05.320
For

00:08:05.320 --> 00:08:06.710
all the religious ones out

00:08:06.720 --> 00:08:08.150
there: Oh my gosh, I can't believe... No,

00:08:08.160 --> 00:08:10.510
no, no. I have fun with my son

00:08:10.520 --> 00:08:14.110
and we play as

00:08:14.110 --> 00:08:14.120
a team.

00:08:14.120 --> 00:08:16.990
Braden wins;

00:08:17.000 --> 00:08:18.790
he's very good at Call

00:08:18.800 --> 00:08:21.310
of Duty. I'm not so good.

00:08:22.560 --> 00:08:24.710
I was really focused and wasn't

00:08:24.720 --> 00:08:26.590
paying attention, but I told Paisley to put

00:08:26.590 --> 00:08:26.600
the

00:08:26.600 --> 00:08:29.230
dog up several times. It was a

00:08:29.240 --> 00:08:30.870
brand new puppy

00:08:30.880 --> 00:08:33.589
and she had it wrapped in a blanket.

00:08:33.599 --> 00:08:36.190
I jumped up to go to the

00:08:36.200 --> 00:08:38.230
bathroom

00:08:38.240 --> 00:08:40.430
in between matches.

00:08:41.840 --> 00:08:43.950
I'm a big guy, of

00:08:43.960 --> 00:08:46.030
course, and I stepped on

00:08:46.040 --> 00:08:48.910
this puppy and killed it

00:08:48.920 --> 00:08:51.790
right there. Squashed it.

00:08:51.800 --> 00:08:54.030
The guts popped out. I mean, this is how

00:08:54.040 --> 00:08:57.750
I squashed and destroyed this dog

00:08:57.760 --> 00:08:59.350
right there.

00:08:59.360 --> 00:09:01.910
Instantaneously, Paisley

00:09:01.910 --> 00:09:01.920
is

00:09:01.920 --> 00:09:04.590
like,

00:09:04.590 --> 00:09:04.600
'You—'because

00:09:04.600 --> 00:09:07.150
the dog is dead.

00:09:07.160 --> 00:09:09.870
I lost it. I'm cussing, acting a

00:09:09.880 --> 00:09:12.830
fool, because I'm so mad about what I

00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:14.950
just did. I'm blaming myself, but

00:09:14.960 --> 00:09:16.710
instantaneously you start

00:09:16.720 --> 00:09:18.110
blaming other people.

00:09:18.110 --> 00:09:18.120
'It's

00:09:18.120 --> 00:09:19.590
your fault.'No, it's my fault. I

00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:21.150
was stupid. I should have watched where I

00:09:21.160 --> 00:09:23.670
was walking.

00:09:23.680 --> 00:09:26.310
But I lost my cool and started saying

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:28.630
all kinds of profanity. I

00:09:28.630 --> 00:09:28.640
was

00:09:28.640 --> 00:09:30.590
freaking out because the dog

00:09:30.600 --> 00:09:33.110
we just bought for Christmas

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:35.030
was dead; it

00:09:35.030 --> 00:09:35.040
had been

00:09:35.040 --> 00:09:37.630
squashed.

00:09:37.640 --> 00:09:38.710
This was years ago.

00:09:41.760 --> 00:09:43.430
I just want to clarify that this was

00:09:43.440 --> 00:09:47.670
a long time ago.

00:09:49.200 --> 00:09:51.590
You don't have to defend me;

00:09:53.840 --> 00:09:56.190
it is what it is. I was a

00:09:56.200 --> 00:09:57.630
jerk

00:09:57.640 --> 00:10:00.510
and killed the dog. I lost

00:10:00.510 --> 00:10:00.520
it. I went

00:10:00.520 --> 00:10:04.190
in the back

00:10:04.200 --> 00:10:07.070
and Paisley started screaming, 'Daddy,

00:10:07.080 --> 00:10:08.790
aren't you going to pray for my dog to

00:10:08.790 --> 00:10:08.800
rise

00:10:08.800 --> 00:10:11.190
from the dead?

00:10:11.200 --> 00:10:13.590
Daddy, don't you believe God will raise

00:10:13.600 --> 00:10:15.550
my dog from the

00:10:15.550 --> 00:10:15.560
dead?'I

00:10:15.560 --> 00:10:17.830
said, 'God's not going to hear me

00:10:17.840 --> 00:10:19.670
at all. Honey, I'm not

00:10:19.680 --> 00:10:22.350
there. I lost it. I'm just not

00:10:22.350 --> 00:10:22.360
there.'I

00:10:22.360 --> 00:10:25.110
said, 'But you pray;

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:27.150
I can't.'She said, 'All things are

00:10:27.160 --> 00:10:31.830
possible to him who believes, Daddy.

00:10:31.840 --> 00:10:35.750
Pray for my dog to get up from the dead.'I told

00:10:35.750 --> 00:10:35.760
her I couldn't

00:10:35.760 --> 00:10:37.510
do it and that

00:10:37.510 --> 00:10:37.520
He wouldn't

00:10:37.520 --> 00:10:39.390
hear me.

00:10:39.400 --> 00:10:41.430
So she started marching up and down the

00:10:41.440 --> 00:10:43.350
hallway,

00:10:43.360 --> 00:10:46.430
screaming as loud as she could, 'All

00:10:46.440 --> 00:10:47.950
things are possible!'praying in the

00:10:47.960 --> 00:10:49.550
Holy Spirit, 'Get up from

00:10:49.560 --> 00:10:51.030
the dead, dog! Get up from the dead!'She

00:10:51.030 --> 00:10:51.040
was

00:10:51.040 --> 00:10:52.630
weeping because her dog

00:10:52.630 --> 00:10:52.640
was

00:10:52.640 --> 00:10:55.750
dead.

00:10:55.760 --> 00:10:58.270
Several hours later, Diana put the dog

00:10:58.280 --> 00:11:00.710
in a shoebox. It was frozen

00:11:00.720 --> 00:11:02.990
outside with snow on

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:05.110
the ground, and

00:11:05.120 --> 00:11:06.350
I thought, 'I'm not going to

00:11:06.360 --> 00:11:07.950
go out there and dig a hole in that

00:11:07.960 --> 00:11:09.550
frozen ground right now.'So we put the

00:11:09.560 --> 00:11:11.990
dog in a shoebox and set it by

00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:13.630
the trash can

00:11:13.640 --> 00:11:14.910
on the

00:11:14.920 --> 00:11:16.910
front porch. I told her I'd take care of it later. Diana put the dog out there and

00:11:28.640 --> 00:11:30.990
I felt bad

00:11:30.990 --> 00:11:31.000
later.

00:11:31.000 --> 00:11:32.430
The Holy Spirit jumped all over me

00:11:32.430 --> 00:11:32.440
because I had

00:11:32.440 --> 00:11:36.110
acted like an idiot.

00:11:37.400 --> 00:11:40.870
I was broken. I went in and told her I

00:11:40.870 --> 00:11:40.880
was

00:11:40.880 --> 00:11:42.270
sorry. Paisley was still

00:11:42.280 --> 00:11:43.550
crying. I admitted I was an idiot

00:11:43.550 --> 00:11:43.560
and

00:11:43.560 --> 00:11:45.030
apologized

00:11:45.040 --> 00:11:47.310
for

00:11:47.310 --> 00:11:47.320
yelling.

00:11:47.320 --> 00:11:49.270
Then

00:11:49.280 --> 00:11:52.670
Diana went to take the trash out

00:11:52.680 --> 00:11:54.310
to

00:11:54.320 --> 00:11:57.910
the porch, and the dog was gone.

00:11:57.920 --> 00:12:00.030
She came in

00:12:00.030 --> 00:12:00.040
and said,

00:12:00.040 --> 00:12:02.110
'Brandon, the dog

00:12:02.120 --> 00:12:04.870
is gone. Something got

00:12:04.880 --> 00:12:07.470
it.'I

00:12:07.480 --> 00:12:09.110
thought because

00:12:09.110 --> 00:12:09.120
we lived

00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:10.829
in the country, raccoons or a stray cat had

00:12:10.839 --> 00:12:13.630
taken

00:12:13.640 --> 00:12:16.590
the

00:12:16.600 --> 00:12:18.870
puppy to

00:12:18.870 --> 00:12:18.880
eat

00:12:18.880 --> 00:12:20.430
because it was cold.

00:12:20.440 --> 00:12:23.270
Then

00:12:23.280 --> 00:12:28.870
she heard a squeaking noise.

00:12:31.320 --> 00:12:33.710
Diana went down and looked, and

00:12:33.720 --> 00:12:37.550
that dog was alive. It was frozen cold,

00:12:37.550 --> 00:12:37.560
but

00:12:37.560 --> 00:12:38.750
all

00:12:38.750 --> 00:12:38.760
the

00:12:38.760 --> 00:12:40.550
guts and blood were gone. It was

00:12:40.560 --> 00:12:42.350
completely restored—no guts, no blood, nothing. That dog had been completely mushed; I had crushed the bones, but it was

00:12:42.360 --> 00:12:44.390
completely restored

00:12:52.839 --> 00:12:57.510
by the power of God.

00:12:57.520 --> 00:12:59.590
Diana brought the dog in,

00:12:59.600 --> 00:13:01.430
started blow-drying it, and got it

00:13:01.440 --> 00:13:03.590
warm. Paisley sat there

00:13:03.600 --> 00:13:05.670
with the biggest grin on her face and

00:13:05.680 --> 00:13:08.870
said, 'Daddy, I told you all things

00:13:08.880 --> 00:13:14.190
are possible to him who

00:13:14.200 --> 00:13:22.070
believes.'To

00:13:22.080 --> 00:13:25.790
this day,

00:13:25.800 --> 00:13:27.750
I'll never forget her little face,

00:13:27.750 --> 00:13:27.760
nor

00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:30.270
your face, nor

00:13:30.270 --> 00:13:30.280
Braden's

00:13:30.280 --> 00:13:31.829
face.

00:13:31.839 --> 00:13:33.630
We were

00:13:33.640 --> 00:13:35.230
all in awe of

00:13:35.240 --> 00:13:37.270
the goodness of God

00:13:37.270 --> 00:13:37.280
and

00:13:37.280 --> 00:13:40.070
the shock of what

00:13:40.080 --> 00:13:43.310
had happened. I held that dog in my

00:13:43.320 --> 00:13:45.350
hand, and God spoke to me. He said,

00:13:45.360 --> 00:13:47.710
'Even on your best day, son, your

00:13:47.720 --> 00:13:54.310
righteousness is filthy rags.

00:13:54.320 --> 00:13:56.670
In the natural, without my Son's

00:13:56.680 --> 00:13:59.829
blood, you're never good

00:13:59.839 --> 00:14:03.910
enough.'God

00:14:03.920 --> 00:14:06.910
brought that back to me today

00:14:06.910 --> 00:14:06.920
regarding

00:14:06.920 --> 00:14:12.710
the mantle we walk in.

00:14:12.720 --> 00:14:14.990
No matter how you live your life,

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:17.910
it's about keeping a

00:14:17.920 --> 00:14:19.630
relationship with Him and keeping the

00:14:19.640 --> 00:14:22.110
main thing the main thing,

00:14:22.120 --> 00:14:26.310
but not touching the trigger.

00:14:26.320 --> 00:14:28.390
What's God's trigger? Touching the

00:14:28.400 --> 00:14:29.710
glory.

00:14:29.720 --> 00:14:32.750
Apart from Him, Jesus said, 'I only

00:14:32.760 --> 00:14:34.630
do what my Father tells me to

00:14:36.430 --> 00:14:36.440
do.'He

00:14:40.160 --> 00:14:42.510
did not separate Himself from His

00:14:42.520 --> 00:14:44.510
Father's voice

00:14:44.520 --> 00:14:46.750
but always

00:14:46.760 --> 00:14:50.110
deflected and gave God the praise. If the Son

00:14:50.120 --> 00:14:53.510
of God always gave God the

00:14:53.520 --> 00:14:54.750
praise, we

00:14:54.750 --> 00:14:54.760
must

00:14:54.760 --> 00:14:57.510
do the same. In everything you do

00:14:59.440 --> 00:15:01.550
in

00:15:01.560 --> 00:15:03.790
word and deed, give all to the glory

00:15:03.800 --> 00:15:07.430
of God. The Bible says that in all we do

00:15:07.430 --> 00:15:07.440
and

00:15:07.440 --> 00:15:10.310
say, in word and

00:15:10.310 --> 00:15:10.320
deed,

00:15:10.320 --> 00:15:13.110
give all to the glory of God. No matter

00:15:13.120 --> 00:15:15.910
what you're going through, we

00:15:15.920 --> 00:15:18.710
give all to the glory of God;

00:15:20.959 --> 00:15:22.190
we stay on God's side.

00:15:22.200 --> 00:15:24.870
As I

00:15:24.880 --> 00:15:27.550
walked through that,

00:15:27.560 --> 00:15:29.190
the Lord reminded me—because it was

00:15:29.190 --> 00:15:29.200
around

00:15:29.200 --> 00:15:31.470
the same time

00:15:31.470 --> 00:15:31.480
of

00:15:31.480 --> 00:15:33.470
year,

00:15:33.470 --> 00:15:33.480
January—to

00:15:33.480 --> 00:15:35.670
look

00:15:35.680 --> 00:15:38.630
back at the Rolodex of

00:15:38.640 --> 00:15:41.069
miracles seen

00:15:41.069 --> 00:15:41.079
in

00:15:41.079 --> 00:15:42.630
life.

00:15:42.640 --> 00:15:44.750
You realize that even

00:15:44.750 --> 00:15:44.760
then,

00:15:44.760 --> 00:15:47.069
your righteousness is filthy

00:15:47.079 --> 00:15:48.550
rags. The point

00:15:48.550 --> 00:15:48.560
the Lord

00:15:48.560 --> 00:15:50.350
was

00:15:54.480 --> 00:15:55.829
trying to tell

00:15:55.839 --> 00:15:58.790
me was, 'Brandon, when you give me

00:15:58.800 --> 00:16:00.750
praise, it opens the door for the

00:16:00.760 --> 00:16:02.590
blessing.'When

00:16:02.600 --> 00:16:05.430
you acknowledge Him

00:16:05.430 --> 00:16:05.440
and

00:16:05.440 --> 00:16:07.710
tell people,

00:16:07.720 --> 00:16:10.949
no matter the size of your platform, that

00:16:10.949 --> 00:16:10.959
you

00:16:10.959 --> 00:16:13.829
can't do anything apart from Him, it

00:16:13.829 --> 00:16:13.839
matters.

00:16:13.839 --> 00:16:16.030
Seeing things coming in the

00:16:16.040 --> 00:16:19.150
future is a gift

00:16:19.160 --> 00:16:21.910
from Him to show us what is coming.

00:16:21.920 --> 00:16:24.390
Joel chapter 2 says that young men

00:16:24.400 --> 00:16:26.990
will see visions and old men will dream

00:16:27.000 --> 00:16:29.910
dreams. People ridicule this,

00:16:29.910 --> 00:16:29.920
but

00:16:29.920 --> 00:16:32.230
God

00:16:32.230 --> 00:16:32.240
said,

00:16:32.240 --> 00:16:33.270
'Brandon, I'm

00:16:33.280 --> 00:16:34.829
just fulfilling what I told you I'd do

00:16:34.839 --> 00:16:38.470
in my Word. Someone

00:16:38.470 --> 00:16:38.480
has

00:16:38.480 --> 00:16:40.510
to fit the role;

00:16:40.520 --> 00:16:44.470
why not

00:16:51.839 --> 00:16:53.510
you?'My

00:16:58.200 --> 00:17:00.790
young men will have visions,

00:17:00.800 --> 00:17:02.750
my old men will dream dreams, and I'll

00:17:02.760 --> 00:17:05.630
pour out my Spirit upon my handmaidens.

00:17:05.630 --> 00:17:05.640
Whether

00:17:05.640 --> 00:17:07.510
it's

00:17:07.520 --> 00:17:10.316
Acts chapter 2 or Joel chapter 2, God

00:17:10.316 --> 00:17:10.326
is

00:17:10.326 --> 00:17:11.550
fulfilling

00:17:11.550 --> 00:17:11.560
what

00:17:11.560 --> 00:17:12.829
He said

00:17:12.829 --> 00:17:12.839
He

00:17:12.839 --> 00:17:14.429
would do in the

00:17:14.439 --> 00:17:16.310
last days.

00:17:16.320 --> 00:17:19.429
How many visions

00:17:19.429 --> 00:17:19.439
qualify?

00:17:19.439 --> 00:17:23.150
'Visions'is

00:17:23.160 --> 00:17:27.669
plural; it

00:17:27.669 --> 00:17:27.679
doesn't

00:17:27.679 --> 00:17:29.750
mean

00:17:29.760 --> 00:17:31.750
singular.

00:17:31.760 --> 00:17:33.669
He's saying multiple.

00:17:33.679 --> 00:17:38.870
Old men will have multiple dreams.

00:17:44.200 --> 00:17:46.950
If you push into Him and give

00:17:46.950 --> 00:17:46.960
Him

00:17:46.960 --> 00:17:48.510
glory,

00:17:48.510 --> 00:17:48.520
He

00:17:48.520 --> 00:17:50.350
will

00:17:50.360 --> 00:17:52.830
show you much more to come,

00:17:52.840 --> 00:17:54.669
and it will prove accurate. It

00:17:54.679 --> 00:17:57.790
will be a sign for the world

00:17:57.800 --> 00:18:00.550
to know He

00:18:00.550 --> 00:18:00.560
is

00:18:00.560 --> 00:18:01.710
coming.

00:18:01.710 --> 00:18:01.720
The

00:18:01.720 --> 00:18:05.350
main mission

00:18:05.350 --> 00:18:05.360
for

00:18:05.360 --> 00:18:07.590
this channel is to tell

00:18:07.590 --> 00:18:07.600
His

00:18:07.600 --> 00:18:10.350
people He is coming and

00:18:10.350 --> 00:18:10.360
that

00:18:10.360 --> 00:18:13.510
it's time to repent and

00:18:13.520 --> 00:18:16.910
get serious about the Father coming.

00:18:16.910 --> 00:18:16.920
I

00:18:16.920 --> 00:18:18.990
said

00:18:18.990 --> 00:18:19.000
I'd

00:18:19.000 --> 00:18:21.030
do it.

00:18:23.480 --> 00:18:25.830
We set out to

00:18:25.840 --> 00:18:27.990
raise a prayer channel with a

00:18:28.000 --> 00:18:30.750
million prayer warriors

00:18:30.760 --> 00:18:32.630
on YouTube.

00:18:32.630 --> 00:18:32.640
By

00:18:32.640 --> 00:18:34.830
doing so, you will change the

00:18:34.840 --> 00:18:36.990
course of things.

00:18:37.000 --> 00:18:39.909
Stand strong, keep in His Word,

00:18:39.919 --> 00:18:44.270
and always deflect the glory.

00:18:44.280 --> 00:18:45.909
It's not about Brandon

00:18:45.909 --> 00:18:45.919
or

00:18:45.919 --> 00:18:48.190
Diana.

00:18:52.720 --> 00:18:56.190
I will not take His glory.

00:19:01.800 --> 00:19:04.350
Last night

00:19:04.360 --> 00:19:06.710
in the spirit,

00:19:07.960 --> 00:19:10.350
we saw Trump

00:19:10.360 --> 00:19:13.430
negotiating major

00:19:13.440 --> 00:19:17.470
deals with the Greenland people.

00:19:22.480 --> 00:19:25.950
Europe and the EU were standing strong

00:19:25.960 --> 00:19:27.950
against Trump, saying

00:19:27.950 --> 00:19:27.960
they wouldn't

00:19:27.960 --> 00:19:29.149
allow

00:19:29.149 --> 00:19:29.159
it.

00:19:29.159 --> 00:19:33.710
I saw them divided in half. The

00:19:33.710 --> 00:19:33.720
elders in

00:19:33.720 --> 00:19:35.430
Greenland

00:19:38.360 --> 00:19:40.550
did not want to join the United

00:19:40.560 --> 00:19:43.950
States, but the young people did.

00:19:47.280 --> 00:19:49.430
They were going to take a

00:19:49.440 --> 00:19:54.270
major vote to

00:19:54.270 --> 00:19:54.280
become

00:19:54.280 --> 00:19:56.550
part of the

00:19:56.560 --> 00:19:58.470
United States.

00:19:58.480 --> 00:19:59.470
The Trump

00:19:59.480 --> 00:20:01.590
administration was after

00:20:01.600 --> 00:20:03.910
minerals.

00:20:03.920 --> 00:20:06.990
I saw billions of dollars of

00:20:07.000 --> 00:20:09.950
minerals to build batteries and

00:20:09.960 --> 00:20:11.950
things like that.

00:20:13.800 --> 00:20:15.990
What else was in the dirt?

00:20:16.000 --> 00:20:18.670
I saw big dump trucks

00:20:18.670 --> 00:20:18.680
circling

00:20:18.680 --> 00:20:20.790
around; they were

00:20:20.800 --> 00:20:22.190
going down and getting the

00:20:22.200 --> 00:20:23.430
minerals.

00:20:23.440 --> 00:20:25.710
I saw fish,

00:20:27.280 --> 00:20:29.750
which I thought related to cobalt.

00:20:36.200 --> 00:20:37.150
You're still

00:20:37.160 --> 00:20:38.710
going, right? No, I want you to

00:20:38.720 --> 00:20:40.270
tell me.

00:20:42.280 --> 00:20:43.830
We'll bring our American stores to your

00:20:43.840 --> 00:20:44.230
shores.

00:20:44.240 --> 00:20:46.550
I saw

00:20:46.550 --> 00:20:46.560
American

00:20:46.560 --> 00:20:50.430
stores and big companies going to Greenland

00:20:50.440 --> 00:20:53.270
to make it like America, like

00:20:53.280 --> 00:20:55.670
we would do anywhere else.

00:20:55.680 --> 00:20:57.950
You're part of us now, so

00:20:57.960 --> 00:21:00.390
we'll share what we have.

00:21:00.400 --> 00:21:01.870
An IHOP is going to come

00:21:01.880 --> 00:21:02.870
there,

00:21:02.880 --> 00:21:04.670
or a Denny's

00:21:04.670 --> 00:21:04.680
where

00:21:04.680 --> 00:21:06.774
you can eat breakfast at night.

00:21:11.480 --> 00:21:13.270
McDonald's is probably already there.

00:21:13.280 --> 00:21:14.790
Starbucks is just around the corner on

00:21:14.800 --> 00:21:16.599
every block.

00:21:22.200 --> 00:21:25.190
I cracked myself up; it's

00:21:25.200 --> 00:21:27.310
not even funny, but it's funny to me.

00:21:28.389 --> 00:21:28.399
Dunkin'Donuts

00:21:28.640 --> 00:21:31.670
is going right next door.

00:21:33.200 --> 00:21:36.150
I saw all these major things

00:21:36.160 --> 00:21:37.150
coming.

00:21:37.160 --> 00:21:39.470
This is what we saw last night.

00:21:39.480 --> 00:21:42.910
Less than 24 hours, folks, and it happens in

00:21:42.920 --> 00:21:44.510
the news.

00:21:44.520 --> 00:21:46.750
A lot

00:21:46.760 --> 00:21:48.550
of times, when we would see things in

00:21:48.560 --> 00:21:50.390
the past before we started getting

00:21:50.400 --> 00:21:51.510
on the channel,

00:21:51.520 --> 00:21:53.870
some things

00:21:53.880 --> 00:21:55.870
would take two to three months or two to

00:21:55.880 --> 00:21:58.070
three years. He warned

00:21:58.080 --> 00:22:00.270
us about COVID before we were even on

00:22:00.280 --> 00:22:02.030
YouTube.

00:22:02.040 --> 00:22:03.030
He told us that summer that

00:22:03.030 --> 00:22:03.040
a

00:22:03.040 --> 00:22:04.669
major shaking was coming, and

00:22:04.679 --> 00:22:07.110
it started happening by

00:22:07.120 --> 00:22:11.350
March of

00:22:13.640 --> 00:22:15.390
2019,

00:22:15.400 --> 00:22:17.710
I think. He spoke to us in

00:22:17.720 --> 00:22:19.830
2018.

00:22:19.830 --> 00:22:19.840
He

00:22:19.840 --> 00:22:21.669
told us COVID was coming, and

00:22:21.679 --> 00:22:23.030
then he told us another virus is coming

00:22:23.040 --> 00:22:24.470
after that.

00:22:28.040 --> 00:22:29.630
Read

00:22:34.320 --> 00:22:35.830
that one right there:

00:22:35.840 --> 00:22:38.390
'Trump admin reportedly

00:22:38.400 --> 00:22:40.950
considers paying each Greenland resident

00:22:40.960 --> 00:22:45.470
up to 100k amid US takeover

00:22:45.470 --> 00:22:45.480
talks'—that

00:22:45.480 --> 00:22:47.790
came out today. How much did I tell you

00:22:47.800 --> 00:22:49.510
they would offer them?

00:22:55.720 --> 00:22:58.510
I saw

00:22:58.510 --> 00:22:58.520
that

00:22:58.520 --> 00:23:00.230
the real agreement, whenever it really

00:23:00.240 --> 00:23:03.910
