00:23:08.160 --> 00:23:11.390
per citizen

00:23:11.400 --> 00:23:13.950
to buy their country with our US tax

00:23:13.960 --> 00:23:17.190
dollars.

00:23:17.200 --> 00:23:20.630
I saw these major things

00:23:20.630 --> 00:23:20.640
taking

00:23:20.640 --> 00:23:23.150
place last night in prayer, and it's in the

00:23:23.160 --> 00:23:25.990
news today, less than 12 hours

00:23:26.000 --> 00:23:27.110
later.

00:23:27.120 --> 00:23:28.270
People ask, 'Do you work at

00:23:28.280 --> 00:23:30.590
the news agency, Brandon? How did you

00:23:30.600 --> 00:23:32.750
know that? Do you work for the

00:23:32.750 --> 00:23:32.760
CIA?'I've

00:23:32.760 --> 00:23:34.510
heard that so much lately.

00:23:34.520 --> 00:23:36.910
'You must be Mossad. You work for

00:23:36.920 --> 00:23:39.950
Mossad. CIA, you're an operative. I

00:23:39.960 --> 00:23:41.550
know you are. You're part

00:23:41.560 --> 00:23:42.350
of the

00:23:42.360 --> 00:23:45.550
Masonics, part of that 666 stuff

00:23:45.560 --> 00:23:48.110
with the

00:23:48.110 --> 00:23:48.120
witchcraft.'Come

00:23:48.120 --> 00:23:50.270
on, folks.

00:23:50.280 --> 00:23:52.830
I'm a Holy Ghost believer,

00:23:52.840 --> 00:23:54.390
baptized in the Holy Ghost, praying in the

00:23:54.400 --> 00:23:56.630
Holy Ghost. I'm not CIA. I don't work

00:23:56.640 --> 00:24:00.510
for Mossad. It's Jesus.

00:24:00.520 --> 00:24:02.790
Isn't he wonderful?

00:24:02.800 --> 00:24:05.070
That's all I can

