Billy Burke and Billye Brim, my BBs.

02:09:38.640 --> 02:09:41.510
But

02:09:41.520 --> 02:09:43.190
we don't do a lot, do we?

02:09:43.200 --> 02:09:44.830
We kind of just do our thing. Praying

02:09:44.830 --> 02:09:44.840
in

02:09:44.840 --> 02:09:47.950
here is a

02:09:47.950 --> 02:09:47.960
lot—the

02:09:47.960 --> 02:09:50.510
emails and all the stuff we get by

